butions. In other words, the angular power\nspectrum could be both positive or negative, depending on the positive biasing\nor antibiasing, respectively. Detection of the cross-correlation thus offers a\nnew opportunity to observationally understand the reionization history of\nintergalactic medium connected to the dark matter clustering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Oct 2001 07:58:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2001 23:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
